item.description: WG’s flagship facility is located in Uruguay where the Company will benefit from favourable marijuana and patent regimes, and a low cost location for production. The Facility includes: •20 Acre Farm (expanding to 1000 acres) •A 5,400 sq. ft. Greenhouse • State-of-the-art lab and in-house patent office. This is the only lab in the country that allows for formulation and full spectrum cannabinoid research
